					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						<h4>About Expero</h4>
						
<p class="p1">With offices in Austin and Houston, Texas, Expero is a software consulting firm with 15 years’ experience bringing challenging ideas to real software in complex domains. Our skill is taking high impact, high complexity research ideas and turning them into deployable, usable software, maintained over many years. Our starting points are quant spreadsheets, massively parallel simulations, chalkboard sketches, and academic papers, whose ideas have not been or cannot be implemented in off-the-shelf software. We turn these into web-deployed software that brings this functionality to the masses.</p>

